Just checked. Create table is also supported.
@findepi do we have a test coverage for that? Quickly I could not find any.
Something as simple as
    @Test
    public void testCreateTable()
    {
        getQueryRunner().execute("CREATE TABLE t (c BIGINT)");
        getQueryRunner().execute("INSERT INTO t VALUES(10)");
        assertThat(query("SELECT CAST(c as VARCHAR) from t")).matches("VALUES (VARCHAR '10')");
    }
or
    @Test
    public void testCreateTable()
    {
        getQueryRunner().execute("CREATE TABLE t (c BIGINT)");
        assertThat(query("DESCRIBE t")).matches(results -> results.getRowCount() > 0);
    }
